        {
            "id": "s8_5_7",
            "type": "text",
            "title": "repeat Loop (Bonus)",
            "content": "`repeat` creates an infinite loop that must be exited with `break`.\n\n```r\ncount <- 1\nrepeat {\n  print(count)\n  count <- count + 1\n  if (count > 5) break\n}\n```"
        },
        {
            "id": "s8_5_8",
            "type": "code",
            "title": "repeat Example",
            "content": "Run:",
            "codeSnippet": "x <- 1\nrepeat {\n  print(x)\n  x <- x + 1\n  if (x > 3) break\n}",
            "codeLanguage": "r",
            "canRunCode": true
        }
